items.title: Former NYC Mayor Rudy Giuliani injured in car accident
items.description: The former Trump adviser's car was struck from behind on a highway in New Hampshire, a statement said.

items.title: Hamas spokesman Abu Obeida killed in Gaza, Israel says
items.description: The military spokesman was killed in strikes on Saturday, Israel says - Hamas has not confirmed the death.

items.title: UK closes embassy in Cairo amid row over activist's arrest
items.description: The removal of the barriers is widely seen as retaliation for the arrest of a pro-Egyptian government activist in London last week.

items.title: Head-on crash between police van and prison bus kills 16 in Namibia
items.description: Fourteen prison and police officers, along with two civilians, were killed in the crash.

items.title: 'I fear for my sons': Mother awaits DNA results on remains linked to Kenya's starvation cult
items.description: Carolyne Odour's two young sons went missing with their father - a follower of self-proclaimed pastor Paul Mackenzie.
